DESCRIPTION:Link:&nbsp\;https://om.rs/zoommf<br><br>Goal: A focused call wi
 th community members on Appointment requirements. At the moment\, the think
 ing is that we could leverage existing functionality in Bahmni Appointments
 . But we want to clearly understand the workflow requirements folks have in
  mind.<br><br>Reason: Palladium\, UCSF\, PIH-Peru\, and other orgs have all
  expressed interest recently. Specifically\, PIH-Peru has a site who wants 
 to go live w/ appointments in 3.x\, and Palladium would like to start work 
 on this within the next 2 weeks.<p><br></p>
