DESCRIPTION:Event Name: Interview - 1st Round\nEvent Description: Hello\,Th
 ank you for showing interest in a role with us at Chase!In this interview r
 ound\, we’re going to ask you to write code live. You should prepare an emp
 ty project in your preferred IDE\, with your favourite programming language
 \, build tool and test libraries.During the interview\, we’ll ask you to sh
 are your screen\, send you a written description of the problem\, and watch
  you code live while you explain what you’re doing.The focus in this step i
 s on code design\, so you should model domain concepts with a level of abst
 raction that’s maintainable and flexible.The interview should take between 
 30 - 60 mins. TLDR\;- Please prepare\, before the interview\, an empty code
  project in your favourite IDE\, testing libraries\, build tool\, programmi
 ng language.- During the interview\, we’ll ask you to write code based on a
  simple scenario.-You will be evaluated on modelling the domain in a mainta
 inable and flexible wayThank you\, and good luck!\nDate & Time: 04:00pm - 0
 5:00pm (UK\, Ireland\, Lisbon Time) on Tuesday\, February 28\, 2023\nLocati
 on: This is a Google Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from y
 our computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/6701ccc
 5-55d1-45e0-98a0-ef2efe11c3ca/google_meet\n\nCancellation Policy: When canc
 elling or rescheduling\, please use the 'reschedule or cancel' option and l
 et your recruiter know rather than booking a new interview instance. \nThan
 k you! \n\nNeed to make changes to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.co
 m/cancellations/c144bf78-103f-47f4-809c-16d240f57c50\nReschedule: https://c
 alendly.com/reschedulings/c144bf78-103f-47f4-809c-16d240f57c50\n
