 at works for you among the ones you see available and you'll receive an inv
 ite with a link to the Hangouts session.<br><br>Please add a note with the 
 topic(s) you'd like to discuss together and\, optionally\, your LinkedIn pr
 ofile so we can connect.<br><br>Talk to you soon\,<br><br>Luca<br><br>Locat
 ion: This is a Google Meet web conference.<br>You can join this meeting fro
 m your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.<br><a href="https://calendly.com/
 events/EIGHM4HOM4JYS3YS/google_meet">https://calendly.com/events/EIGHM4HOM4
 JYS3YS/google_meet</a><br><br>Please share anything that will help prepare 
 for our meeting.:<br>Hello Luca \,<br>Nice to meet you here.<br>My name is 
 Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend developer from Moscow\, Russia.<br>https:
 //www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/<br><br>My current desire is to move 
 to Germany and improve my IT knowledge.<br><br>If it is possible\, I would 
 like to ask you to help me. May be you can recommend something and help me.
 <br>1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernetes\, CI/CD. I want to underst
 and how to work with them\, because a lot of job positions require these te
 chnologies.<br>2) how I can solve algorithm tasks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert 
 effectively to pass an interview in FAANG in the future.<br>3) how I can im
 prove my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Boot framework\, Postgres datab
 ase\, SQL to develop modern applications.<br>4) how I can improve my unders
 tanding of Microservice architecture. I want to know how to develop perfect
  architecture.<br>5) how I can improve my CV and LinkedIn profile to be int
 eresting for recruters and IT companies.<br>6) how I can improve my career 
 path. I can imagine that it is good idea to move to the USA because there a
 re a lot of interesting companies\, projects\, people and so on. I would li
 ke to discuss it.<br>7) how I can relocate to Europe or The USA. May be I u
 se LinkedIn and speak with recruters in wrong way. I would like to discuss 
