CREATED:20210827T183843Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Dennis\n\nHi!\n\n
 Thanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are excited to g
 et to know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\n \n\nWhat's 
 next?\n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for you. Once you’
 ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google Hangout link. 
 Once the session started and we are both in\, I will give you a brief intro
  about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in mind. Hop
 efully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\n \n\nLookin
 g forward to meet you\n\nDennis\n\nLocation: This is a Google Meet web conf
 erence.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or smartph
 one.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/CJFAUUJHOBDVOVP5/google_meet\n\nPlease sh
 are anything that will help us to have a great conversation: Specify your c
 hallenge\, list questions etc. * :\nHello Dennis\,\nNice to meet you here.\
 nMy name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend developer from Moscow\, Russi
 a.\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/\n\nMy current desire is to
  move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge.\n\nIf it is possible\, I woul
 d like to ask you to help me. May be you can recommend something and help m
 e.\n1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernetes\, CI/CD. I want to underst
 and how to work with them\, because a lot of job positions require these te
 chnologies.\n2) how I can solve algorithm tasks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert ef
 fectively to pass an interview in FAANG in the future.\n3) how I can improv
 e my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Boot framework\, Postgres database\
 , SQL to develop modern applications.\n4) how I can improve my understandin
 g of Microservice architecture. I want to know how to develop perfect archi
 tecture.\n5) how I can improve my CV and LinkedIn profile to be interesting
  for recruters and IT companies.\n6) how I can improve my career path. I ca
 n imagine that it is good idea to move to the USA because there are a lot o
 f interesting companies\, projects\, people and so on. I would like to disc
 uss it.\n7) how I can relocate to Europe or The USA. May be I use LinkedIn 
 and speak with recruters in wrong way. I would like to discuss it either.\n
 \nIf we can discuss one of these questions\, write me please\, I will prepa
 re questions for this topic.\n\nBest Regards\nZufar Sunagatov\n\nReschedule
  Reason: Hello Dennis\,\nI hope everything is okay with you.\nI'm sorry\, I
  have to reschedule our meeting because I feel bad.\n\nI really look forwar
 d to our meeting. If it is possible write me which topics we can discuss fr
 om my list before our next meeting.\n\nBest regards\nZufar\n\nNeed to make 
 changes to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/DOGYPBTN
 TBGJKMFT\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/DOGYPBTNTBGJKMFT\n
 \nPowered by Calendly.com\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https:/
 /meet.google.com/ncr-tfvv-upw\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.
 google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~
 :~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 ::~:~::-
