DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Kate<br><br>Hi!<b
 r><br>Thanks for subscribing to a mentoring session with me. I am excited t
 o get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.<br><br>&nbsp
 \;<br><br>What's next?<br><br>Please select the date and time that works be
 st for you. Once you’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a 
 Google Hangout link. Once the session started and we are both in\, I will g
 ive you a brief intro about myself so that we can jump right into whatever 
 you have in mind. Hopefully\, you can take as much as possible out of this 
 session.<br><br>&nbsp\;<br><br>Looking forward to meeting you<br><br>Kate<b
 r><br>Location: This is a Google Meet web conference.<br>You can join this 
 meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.<br><a href="https://ca
 lendly.com/events/BJCBOTUOJZLDFGWT/google_meet">https://calendly.com/events
 /BJCBOTUOJZLDFGWT/google_meet</a><br><br>Please share anything that will he
 lp us to have a great conversation: Specify your challenge\, list questions
 \, why did you choose me as a mentor\, etc. *:<br><br>Hello Katerina \,<br>
 Nice to meet you here.<br>My name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend deve
 loper from Moscow\, Russia.<br>https://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/
 <br><br>My current desire is to move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge
 .<br><br>If it is possible\, I would like to ask you to help me. May be you
  can recommend something and help me.<br>1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, 
 Kubernetes\, CI/CD. I want to understand how to work with them\, because a 
 lot of job positions require these technologies.<br>2) how I can solve algo
 rithm tasks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert effectively to pass an interview in FA
 ANG in the future.<br>3) how I can improve my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, 
 Sring Boot framework\, Postgres database\, SQL to develop modern applicatio
 ns.<br>4) how I can improve my understanding of Microservice architecture. 
 I want to know how to develop perfect architecture.<br>5) how I can improve
  my CV and LinkedIn profile to be interesting for recruters and IT companie
 s.<br>6) how I can improve my career path. I can imagine that it is good id
 ea to move to the USA because there are a lot of interesting companies\, pr
 ojects\, people and so on. I would like to discuss it.<br>7) how I can relo
 cate to Europe or The USA. May be I use LinkedIn and speak with recruters i
 n wrong way. I would like to discuss it either.<br><br>If we can discuss on
 e of these questions\, write me please\, I will prepare questions for this 
 topic.<br><br>Best Regards<br>Zufar Sunagatov<br><br>Need to make changes t
 o this event?<br>Cancel: <a href="https://calendly.com/cancellations/BLA5GH
 NJB3VOR3CJ">https://calendly.com/cancellations/BLA5GHNJB3VOR3CJ</a><br>Resc
 hedule: <a href="https://calendly.com/reschedulings/BLA5GHNJB3VOR3CJ">https
 ://calendly.com/reschedulings/BLA5GHNJB3VOR3CJ</a>\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin wi
 th Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/ofg-qjki-krs\n\nLearn more about Me
 et at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not e
 dit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
