DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Connecting on Terminology Management:</strong></p><p
 ><em><strong>Sharing Experiences &amp\; Exploring New Ways to Get Involved<
 /strong></em></p><p>OCL and OpenMRS Dictionary Manager teams are hosting a 
 session during the OpenHIE Terminology Services call on&nbsp\;<strong>Frida
 y 3 June from 9 to 10 am (EDT) / 1-2 pm (UTC)</strong>&nbsp\;to bring toget
 her those who are working on terminology management.</p><p>Participants are
  encouraged to attend\, ready to share approaches\, challenges\, and succes
 ses their team is facing. We will also spend time discussing how we can all
  support each other in this work.</p><p><em>This session will be a very cas
 ual chat\, so no need to prepare any slides!</em></p><p><a href="https://wi
 ki.ohie.org/display/resources/2022-06-03+Terminology+Service+Call"><b><stro
 ng>Learn More &amp\; Join the Call</strong></b></a></p>
