DESCRIPTION:Thank you for your request for a C19 Lateral Flow testing kit\n
 to be sent to your chosen address:85 Hackney House\, London\, DA17 6FD\, Un
 ited KingdomThis confirms your request has\nbeen received and your package 
 will be prepared and shipped during the next\nworking day. Packages are sen
 t by next day delivery (either carrier or Royal\nMail 1st class). Please al
 low up to 3 working days from request to receive your\npackage.If there\nis
  error on shipping address for the delivery of test package #1\, please\nco
 ntact us at: appointments@hcaprimarycare.co.uk 0345 437\n0691 (option 1). I
 f you\nwish to alter your shipping address for future deliveries\, you can 
 update by going to\n'My Account' on the Patient Portal (top right of your s
 creen) and\nupdate accordingly. Unfortunately you cannot amend 1st delivery
  by altering\naddress on My Account. Completing a test is\nstraightforward 
 please click\nhere to see full instructions on how to take your\ntest and s
 ubmit results as well as our FAQ’s and\nwatch the simple instruction Video 
 Click here to watch\nvideo For\neach\ntest please log in to the Patient Por
 tal and enter your results. This is mandatory and\nrequired by Government r
 egulations and results are shared by us to PHE for\nnational contact tracin
 g.If you have submitted\na positive result in error please contact appointm
 ents@hcaprimarycare.co.uk  as soon as possible so we can advise on the\nnex
 t steps. Failure to do so will result in your details being shared to Publi
 c\nHealth England as a positive caseKind regards\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\
 n\n\n\n\n\n\nHCA\nPrimary Care Team
