DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Iuliia<br><br>Hi!
 <br><br>Thanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are exci
 ted to get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.<br><br>
 &nbsp\;<br><br>What's next?<br><br>Please select the date and time that wor
 ks best for you. Once you’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite wi
 th a Google Hangout link. Once the session started and we are both in\, I w
 ill give you a brief intro about myself so that we can jump right into what
 ever you have in mind. Hopefully you can take as much as possible out of th
 is session.<br><br>&nbsp\;<br><br>Looking forward to meet you<br><br>Iuliia
 <br><br>Location: This is a Google Meet web conference.<br>You can join thi
 s meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.<br><a href="https://
 calendly.com/events/CLCFNRUOIGV74UNI/google_meet">https://calendly.com/even
 ts/CLCFNRUOIGV74UNI/google_meet</a><br><br>Please share anything that will 
 help us to have a great conversation: Specify your challenge\, list questio
 ns etc. *:<br><br>Hello Iuliia \,<br>Nice to meet you here.<br>My name is Z
 ufar. I am a java/kotlin backend developer from Moscow\, Russia.<br>https:/
 /www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/<br><br>My current desire is to move t
 o Germany and improve my IT knowledge.<br><br>If it is possible\, I would l
 ike to ask you to help me. May be you can recommend something and help me.<
 br>1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernetes\, CI/CD. I want to understa
 nd how to work with them\, because a lot of job positions require these tec
 hnologies.<br>2) how I can solve algorithm tasks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert e
 ffectively to pass an interview in FAANG in the future.<br>3) how I can imp
 rove my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Boot framework\, Postgres databa
 se\, SQL to develop modern applications.<br>4) how I can improve my underst
 anding of Microservice architecture. I want to know how to develop perfect 
 architecture.<br>5) how I can improve my CV and LinkedIn profile to be inte
 resting for recruters and IT companies.<br>6) how I can improve my career p
 ath. I can imagine that it is good idea to move to the USA because there ar
 e a lot of interesting companies\, projects\, people and so on. I would lik
 e to discuss it.<br>7) how I can relocate to Europe or The USA. May be I us
 e LinkedIn and speak with recruters in wrong way. I would like to discuss i
 t either.<br><br>If we can discuss one of these questions\, write me please
 \, I will prepare questions for this topic.<br><br>Best Regards<br>Zufar Su
 nagatov<br><br>Need to make changes to this event?<br>Cancel: <a href="http
 s://calendly.com/cancellations/HNE5BAKNDHYFUSIF">https://calendly.com/cance
 llations/HNE5BAKNDHYFUSIF</a><br>Reschedule: <a href="https://calendly.com/
 reschedulings/HNE5BAKNDHYFUSIF">https://calendly.com/reschedulings/HNE5BAKN
 DHYFUSIF</a><br><br>Powered by Calendly.com\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Goog
 le Meet: https://meet.google.com/kiv-azgu-juo\n\nLearn more about Meet at: 
 https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit thi
 s section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
