CREATED:20210214T123439Z
DESCRIPTION:https://vk.com/club156201875<br><br>1) Who are we?<br>I guess y
 ou can call us just a bunch of people who are interested in English.<br>2) 
 What is this all about?<br>Practising and learning English\, meeting awesom
 e people\, watching remarkable videos\, discussing and debating\, inspiring
  and getting inspired.<br>3) How to take part?<br>Just come and join us! Bu
 t better make sure you can get by at the Intermediate level. And it's also 
 absolutely free of charge. (That means it costs nothing. Null. Nada. Nix. Z
 ero. Zip. Zilch!)<br>4) When and where does it take place?<br>Every Friday 
 from 19:00 till 21:00.&nbsp\;We swap between two places -&nbsp\;<a href="ht
 tps://vk.com/rgubru">Russian State Library for Young Adults</a>&nbsp\;and&n
 bsp\;<a href="https://vk.com/zilcc">Library at ZIL Culture Center</a>. See&
 nbsp\;<a href="https://vk.com/wall-156201875">the recent posts</a>&nbsp\;to
  know where to go this week.<br>Meetings in RGBM are usually require regist
 ration (free of charge)\, meetings in ZIL Culture Center don't.<br>5) Why F
 riday Point?<br>Because we meet on Fridays and that's the point!\n\n-::~:~:
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~
 :~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/scz-nbrt-qnk\n\nLearn
  more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nP
 lease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
LAST-MODIFIED:20230106T091404Z
LOCATION:ZIL Culture Centre\, Vostochnaya Ulitsa\, 4\, к. 1\, Moskva\, Russ
 ia\, 115280
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Friday Point English Speaking Club
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
