DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Soulaiman\n\nHi!\
 n\nThanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are excited t
 o get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\n\n\nLocat
 ion: This is a Google Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from 
 your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/DJAGN4
 HLTJK4NKTZ/google_meet\n\nPlease share anything that will help prepare for 
 our meeting.:\nHello Soulaiman\,\nNice to meet you here.\nMy name is Zufar.
  I am a java/kotlin backend developer from Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.li
 nkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/\n\nMy current desire is to move to Germany a
 nd improve my IT knowledge.\n\nIf it is possible\, I would like to ask you 
 to help me. May be you can recommend something and help me.\n1) how I can l
 earn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernetes\, CI/CD. I want to understand how to work wi
 th them\, because a lot of job positions require these technologies.\n2) ho
 w I can solve algorithm tasks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert effectively to pass 
 an interview in FAANG in the future.\n3) how I can improve my knowledge of 
 Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Boot framework\, Postgres database\, SQL to develop m
 odern applications.\n4) how I can improve my understanding of Microservice 
 architecture. I want to know how to develop perfect architecture.\n5) how I
  can improve my CV and LinkedIn profile to be interesting for recruters and
  IT companies.\n6) how I can improve my career path. I can imagine that it 
 is good idea to move to the USA because there are a lot of interesting comp
 anies\, projects\, people and so on. I would like to discuss it.\n7) how I 
 can relocate to Europe or The USA. May be I use LinkedIn and speak with rec
 ruters in wrong way. I would like to discuss it either.\n\nIf we can discus
 s one of these questions\, write me please\, I will prepare questions for t
 his topic.\n\nBest Regards\nZufar Sunagatov\n\nNeed to make changes to this
  event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/ALDYFE57GIWUKVHE\nResch
 edule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/ALDYFE57GIWUKVHE\n\nPowered by Ca
 lendly.com\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.co
 m/bvx-aaoh-otg\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/us
 ers/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
