DESCRIPTION:Event Name: Mentoring Session with Luca Fiaschi\n\nHi!\n\nThank
 s for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are excited to get to
  know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\n \n\nWhat's next?
 \n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for you. Once you’ve se
 lected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google Hangout link. Once 
 the session started and we are both in\, I will give you a brief intro abou
 t myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in mind. Hopefull
 y you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\n \n\nLooking for
 ward to meet you\n\nLuca Fiaschi\n\n\n\nLocation: This is a Google Meet web
  conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or sm
 artphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/DIBGPUXNPLUJVAPE/google_meet\n\nPlea
 se share anything that will help us to have a great conversation: Specify y
 our challenge\, list questions etc. *:\nHello! My name is Zufar.\nI am an J
 ava/Kotlin software engineer from Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.linkedin.co
 m/in/zufar-sunagatov/\nI would like to grow as a professional\, so I need a
  mentor to define my development path.\nI mean that there are a lot of cour
 ces\, certification and companies where I can grow from a common backend de
 veloper to CTO of big company. I would like to discuss possible ways which 
 steps I should pass.\n\nCancellation Reason: Hi Zufar\, unfortunately\, due
  to a business meeting I would have to cancel this event\n\nPowered by Cale
 ndly.com\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/
 oqr-fvtp-yan\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/user
 s/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
