DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Joaquin Gonzalez\n\nHi!\n\n\nT
 hanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me.\n\nWe are excited to
  get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\n \n\nWhat'
 s next?\n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for you.\n\nOnce
  you’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google Hangout l
 ink. Once the session started and we are both in\, I will give you a brief 
 intro about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in mind
 .\n\nHopefully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\n \n
 \nLooking forward to meeting you\,\n\n\nJoaquín\n\nLocation: This is a Goog
 le Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tab
 let\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/GMABK5AILZCQ2VVG/google_m
 eet\n\nPlease share anything that will help prepare for our meeting.:\nHell
 o Joaquín\,\nNice to meet you here.\nMy name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin b
 ackend developer from Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-s
 unagatov/\n\nMy current desire is to move to Germany and improve my IT know
 ledge.\nIf it is possible\, I would like to ask you to help me. May be you 
 can recommend something and help me.\n- how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kube
 rnetes.\n- how I can improve my CV and LinkedIn profile.\n- how I can impro
 ve my career path.\n\nBest Regards\nZufar Sunagatov\n\nNeed to make changes
  to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/ALH2HC6R3ZDAVWS
 R\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/ALH2HC6R3ZDAVWSR\n\nPower
 ed by Calendly.com\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
