CREATED:20210827T190123Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Charles<br><br>Hi
 !<br><br>Thanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are exc
 ited to get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.<br><br
 >&nbsp\;<br><br>What's next?<br><br>Please select the date and time that wo
 rks best for you. Once you’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite w
 ith a Google Hangout link. Once the session started and we are both in\, I 
 will give you a brief intro about myself so that we can jump right into wha
 tever you have in mind. Hopefully you can take as much as possible out of t
 his session.<br><br>&nbsp\;<br><br>Looking forward to meeting you<br><br>Ch
 arles<br><br><br><br>Location: This is a Google Meet web conference.<br>You
  can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.<br><a h
 ref="https://calendly.com/events/CLHBIWVJJJ6EI5YH/google_meet">https://cale
 ndly.com/events/CLHBIWVJJJ6EI5YH/google_meet</a><br><br>Please share anythi
 ng that will help prepare for our meeting.:<br>Hello Charles \,<br>Nice to 
 meet you here.<br>My name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend developer fr
 om Moscow\, Russia.<br>https://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/<br><br>
 My current desire is to move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge.<br><br
 >If it is possible\, I would like to ask you to help me. May be you can rec
 ommend something and help me.<br>1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernet
 es\, CI/CD. I want to understand how to work with them\, because a lot of j
 ob positions require these technologies.<br>2) how I can solve algorithm ta
 sks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert effectively to pass an interview in FAANG in t
 he future.<br>3) how I can improve my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Bo
 ot framework\, Postgres database\, SQL to develop modern applications.<br>4
 ) how I can improve my understanding of Microservice architecture. I want t
 o know how to develop perfect architecture.<br>5) how I can improve my CV a
 nd LinkedIn profile to be interesting for recruters and IT companies.<br>6)
  how I can improve my career path. I can imagine that it is good idea to mo
 ve to the USA because there are a lot of interesting companies\, projects\,
  people and so on. I would like to discuss it.<br>7) how I can relocate to 
 Europe or The USA. May be I use LinkedIn and speak with recruters in wrong 
 way. I would like to discuss it either.<br><br>If we can discuss one of the
 se questions\, write me please\, I will prepare questions for this topic.<b
 r><br>Best Regards<br>Zufar Sunagatov<br><br>Need to make changes to this e
 vent?<br>Cancel: <a href="https://calendly.com/cancellations/DLB4DAKLGI53A2
 7V">https://calendly.com/cancellations/DLB4DAKLGI53A27V</a><br>Reschedule: 
 <a href="https://calendly.com/reschedulings/DLB4DAKLGI53A27V">https://calen
 dly.com/reschedulings/DLB4DAKLGI53A27V</a><br><br>Powered by Calendly.com\n
 \n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/obw-xnvm-ykm
 \n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/928
 2720\n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
