DESCRIPTION:Dear All \n\nBased on your inputs\, we have scheduled the next 
 Scrum of Scrums for February 13 2019 at 5-7 pm UTC.\n\nhttps://talk.openmrs
 .org/t/scrum-of-scrums-2019-q1-save-the-date-febuary-13-2019/20976/4\n\nThe
  call will be conducted using the details below: \nAudio\, Chat\, Screen Sh
 aring (latest Chrome\, Firefox\, Safari\, or other WebRTC-compatible browse
 rs): http://www.uberconference.com/openmrs\n\nAudio Only (Telephone or your
  favorite VoIP client) Toll-free (United States): +1 (888) 510-4073 Interna
 tional: +1 (201) 479-2055 \n\nView a list of local access phone numbers for
  various countries. After dialing\, when prompted enter meeting number 888-
 510-4073. \n\nAgenda and format of the meeting: \n\nIntroductions \nThe obj
 ective of the call \nA brief presentation on the role of the TPM and new di
 rections for the Roadmap \nPresentations\n\nNext Steps \nAOB \n\nWith Refer
 ence to the presentation format\, we kindly ask each presenter to use the f
 ollowing as a guideline: \nHighlights since the last Scrum \nUpcoming activ
 ities for the next quarter \nCollaboration Opportunities
LAST-MODIFIED:20230524T192556Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Scrum of Scrums
