DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Florian Gamper\n\
 nHi!\n\nThanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are exci
 ted to get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\n \n\
 nWhat's next?\n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for you. O
 nce you’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google Hangou
 t link. Once the session started and we are both in\, I will give you a bri
 ef intro about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in m
 ind. Hopefully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\n \n
 \nLooking forward to meet you\n\nFlorian Gamper\n\nLocation: This is a Goog
 le Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tab
 let\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/ELGAK6BJQPW3X7TT/google_m
 eet\n\nPlease share anything that will help prepare for our meeting. Specif
 y your challenge\, list questions etc.:\nHello Florian\,\nNice to meet you 
 here.\nMy name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend developer from Moscow\,
  Russia.\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/\n\nMy current desire
  is to move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge.\n\nIf it is possible\, 
 I would like to ask you to help me. May be you can recommend something and 
 help me.\n1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernetes\, CI/CD. I want to u
 nderstand how to work with them\, because a lot of job positions require th
 ese technologies.\n2) how I can solve algorithm tasks in Leetcode\, Algoexp
 ert effectively to pass an interview in FAANG in the future.\n3) how I can 
 improve my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Boot framework\, Postgres dat
 abase\, SQL to develop modern applications.\n4) how I can improve my unders
 tanding of Microservice architecture. I want to know how to develop perfect
  architecture.\n5) how I can improve my CV and LinkedIn profile to be inter
 esting for recruters and IT companies.\n6) how I can improve my career path
 . I can imagine that it is good idea to move to the USA because there are a
  lot of interesting companies\, projects\, people and so on. I would like t
 o discuss it.\n7) how I can relocate to Europe or The USA. May be I use Lin
 kedIn and speak with recruters in wrong way. I would like to discuss it eit
 her.\n\nIf we can discuss one of these questions\, write me please\, I will
  prepare questions for this topic.\n\nBest Regards\nZufar Sunagatov\n\nNeed
  to make changes to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations
 /DJF4CB22CO32JLZV\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/DJF4CB22C
 O32JLZV\n\nPowered by Calendly.com\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet
 : https://meet.google.com/syc-vgyb-vsd\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https:/
 /support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit this secti
 on.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
