DESCRIPTION:Hi Zufar! I was drawn to your profile because we both have expe
 rience in developing using Java. Right now I have 1.5 years of developing s
 erver-side using Java Spring Boot\, and my company has plans to migrate to 
 Golang. I need your perspective on the impact of this on my future career\,
  and whether or not I should also branch out to more infra and devops stuff
 . Also\, it would be cool if we can talk about how to set short-term and lo
 ng-term career milestones. Looking forward to our talk!\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJo
 in with ADPList\nhttps://adplist.org/meeting?join=UsUR5e\n\nPlease do not e
 dit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
