DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Sebastian\n\nHi!\
 n\nThanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are excited t
 o get to know you and\n\nwork with you on your current challenge.\n\n\nWhat
 's next?\n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for you. Once y
 ou’ve selected your slot you'll\n\nreceive an invite with a Google Hangout 
 link. Once the session started and we are both in\, I will\n\ngive you a br
 ief intro about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in 
 mind.\n\nHopefully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\
 n\nLooking forward to meeting you\,\n\nSebastian\n\nLocation: This is a Goo
 gle Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, ta
 blet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/APDEI7EITCBFROIH/google_
 meet\n\nPlease share anything that will help us to have a great conversatio
 n: specify your challenge\, list questions etc.:\nHello Sebastian \,\nNice 
 to meet you here.\nMy name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend developer f
 rom Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/\n\nMy cu
 rrent desire is to move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge.\n\nIf it is
  possible\, I would like to ask you to help me. May be you can recommend so
 mething and help me.\n1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernetes\, CI/CD.
  I want to understand how to work with them\, because a lot of job position
 s require these technologies.\n2) how I can solve algorithm tasks in Leetco
 de\, Algoexpert effectively to pass an interview in FAANG in the future.\n3
 ) how I can improve my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Boot framework\, 
 Postgres database\, SQL to develop modern applications.\n4) how I can impro
 ve my understanding of Microservice architecture. I want to know how to dev
 elop perfect architecture.\n5) how I can improve my CV and LinkedIn profile
  to be interesting for recruters and IT companies.\n6) how I can improve my
  career path. I can imagine that it is good idea to move to the USA because
  there are a lot of interesting companies\, projects\, people and so on. I 
 would like to discuss it.\n7) how I can relocate to Europe or The USA. May 
 be I use LinkedIn and speak with recruters in wrong way. I would like to di
 scuss it either.\n\nIf we can discuss one of these questions\, write me ple
 ase\, I will prepare questions for this topic.\n\nBest Regards\nZufar Sunag
 atov\n\nNeed to make changes to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/c
 ancellations/CKG7DB67HABDNCKH\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulin
 gs/CKG7DB67HABDNCKH\n\nPowered by Calendly.com\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with
  Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/eva-pdfs-neo\n\nLearn more about Meet
  at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edi
 t this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
LAST-MODIFIED:20230106T091440Z
