UID:68s5piu5i69o6nu9fio275o6o7@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID:20201209T130000Z
CREATED:20230524T192507Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Weekly PAT call : <a href="https://tinyurl.com/y6kvsot7" tar
 get="_blank">https://tinyurl.com/y6kvsot7</a></p><p>Announcements of upcomi
 ng call agendas and call details are on <a href="https://talk.openmrs.org/c
 /software/bahmni" target="_blank">https://talk.openmrs.org/c/software/bahmn
 i</a>.<br>These posts are tagged with &quot\;bahmni-pat&quot\; and you can 
 see <a href="https://talk.openmrs.org/tags/c/software/bahmni/bahmni-pat" ta
 rget="_blank">a history of them</a>.</p><p>Archive of call notes: <a href="
 https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B-JFKk-8HZXITHJsMDZGV1JESnc?usp=sha
 ring" target="_blank">Google Drive</a></p><p>This is an intersection of pro
 duct thinkers and technical thinkers\, that focuses on how we want to evolv
 e the Bahmni software product. They have regular calls (weekly) to:</p><ul>
 <li>make product direction decisions</li><li>provide guidance to developmen
 t teams who propose new designs (e.g. based on their implementation needs)<
 /li><li>propose the Bahmni Product Roadmap\, for sign-off by the Governing 
 Committee</li></ul><p>Anyone is welcome to participate in these calls\, and
  we’re especially looking for senior technical folks\, anyone who can provi
 de input into a wide range of new features\, and generally anyone who can t
 hink with a “product hat”.</p><p><br></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230524T192507Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bahmni Product Architecture Team call
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC
END:VEVENT
