 s old.\n  - 4 years of Java Software Engineering Experience.\n  - Half of y
 ear Java Software Engineering Experience in the UK. \n  - Bachelor and Mast
 er Degree of Applied Mathematics and Informatics of Samara State Aerospace 
 University. (Let’s consider classic Computer Science Degree). 
