CREATED:20210830T082811Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Kranthi Manchikan
 ti\n\nHi!\n\nThanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are
  excited to get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\
 n \n\nWhat's next?\n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for y
 ou. Once you’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google H
 angout link. Once the session started and we are both in\, I will give you 
 a brief intro about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have
  in mind. Hopefully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n
 \n \n\nLooking forward to meet you\n\nKranthi Manchikanti\n\n\n\nLocation: 
 This is a Google Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your 
 computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/FMHHYRVK7MI
 RPKZ2/google_meet\n\nPlease share anything that will help us to have a grea
 t conversation: Specify your challenge\, list questions etc. :\nHello Krant
 hi \,\nNice to meet you here.\nMy name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend
  developer from Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagat
 ov/\n\nMy current desire is to move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge.
 \n\nIf it is possible\, I would like to ask you to help me. May be you can 
 recommend something and help me.\n1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kuberne
 tes\, CI/CD. I want to understand how to work with them\, because a lot of 
 job positions require these technologies.\n2) how I can solve algorithm tas
 ks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert effectively to pass an interview in FAANG in th
 e future.\n3) how I can improve my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, Sring Boot 
 framework\, Postgres database\, SQL to develop modern applications.\n4) how
  I can improve my understanding of Microservice architecture. I want to kno
 w how to develop perfect architecture.\n5) how I can improve my CV and Link
 edIn profile to be interesting for recruters and IT companies.\n6) how I ca
 n improve my career path. I can imagine that it is good idea to move to the
  USA because there are a lot of interesting companies\, projects\, people a
 nd so on. I would like to discuss it.\n7) how I can relocate to Europe or T
 he USA. May be I use LinkedIn and speak with recruters in wrong way. I woul
 d like to discuss it either.\n\nIf we can discuss one of these questions\, 
 write me please\, I will prepare questions for this topic.\n\nBest Regards\
 nZufar Sunagatov\n\nReschedule Reason: Hi Kranthi\,\nI hope everything is o
 kay with you.\nI am a little ill\, so I have to postpone our meeting. I am 
 sorry for late notification.\n\nBest regards\nZufar\n\nNeed to make changes
  to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/HLB6QJQPM72HZS2
 D\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/HLB6QJQPM72HZS2D\n\nPower
 ed by Calendly.com\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.g
 oogle.com/kvi-rszu-hev\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.
 com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::
 -
