DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Gus Iwanaga\n\nHi
 !\n\n\nThanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me.\n\nWe are ex
 cited to get to know you and work with you on your current challenge. What'
 s next? Please select the date and time that works best for you. Once you’v
 e selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google Hangout link. O
 nce the session started and we are both in\, I will give you a brief intro 
 about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in mind. Hope
 fully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\n\nLooking fo
 rward to meet you!\n\n\nGus\n\nLocation: This is a Google Meet web conferen
 ce.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.
 \nhttps://calendly.com/events/DKFCJZGJO7HP2FZU/google_meet\n\nPlease share 
 anything that will help prepare for our meeting.:\nHello Gustavo\,\nNice to
  meet you here.\nMy name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend developer fro
 m Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/\n\nMy curr
 ent desire is to move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge.\nIf it is pos
 sible\, I would like to ask you to help me. May be you can recommend someth
 ing and help me.\n- how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, Kubernetes.\n- how I can
  improve my CV and LinkedIn profile.\n- how I can improve my career path.\n
 Best Regards\nZufar Sunagatov\n\nNeed to make changes to this event?\nCance
