 r><br><b>Objectives for the session</b>:<br><br><ol><li dir="ltr"><p dir="l
 tr">Explain the relationship between the OpenMRS community\, OpenMRS implem
 entations\, and OpenMRS users.</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Explain h
 ow the OpenMRS community is organized.</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">D
 escribe shared community practices or conventions.</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p
  dir="ltr">Use community tools to get help and make contributions</p></li><
 li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Use community dashboards\, roadmaps\, and project
  pages to identify potential areas of collaboration.</p></li><li dir="ltr">
 <p dir="ltr">Getting help from the right people in the community.</p></li><
 /ol>
