CREATED:20210827T185000Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Vinit Shahdeo\n\n
 Hi!\n\nThanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are excit
 ed to get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\n\nWha
 t's next?\n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for you. Once 
 you’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google Hangout li
 nk. Once the session started and we are both in\, I will give you a brief i
 ntro about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in mind.
  Hopefully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\n \n\nLo
 oking forward to meet you.\n\nVinit Shahdeo\n\nLocation: This is a Google M
 eet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\
 , or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/FOCFISSMLFPLKS6I/google_meet\
 n\nPlease share anything that will help us to have a great conversation: Sp
 ecify your challenge\, list questions etc.:\nHello! My name is Zufar.\nI am
  an Java/Kotlin software engineer from Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.linked
 in.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/\nI would like to grow as a professional\, so I n
 eed a mentor to define my development path.\nI mean that there are a lot of
  cources\, certification and companies where I can grow from a common backe
 nd developer to CTO of big company. I would like to discuss possible ways w
 hich steps I should pass.\n\nNeed to make changes to this event?\nCancel: h
 ttps://calendly.com/cancellations/ALF5HEKNBCLKMI3Z\nReschedule: https://cal
 endly.com/reschedulings/ALF5HEKNBCLKMI3Z\n\nPowered by Calendly.com\n\n\n-:
 :~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/huo-ajhj-knc\n\n
 Learn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
 \n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
