DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Renato Tarantelli
 <br><br>Hi!<br><br><br>Thanks for subscribing to a mentoring session with m
 e. We are excited to get to know you and work with you on your current chal
 lenge.<br><br>&nbsp\;<br><br>What's next?<br><br>Please select the date and
  time that works best for you. Once you’ve selected your slot you'll receiv
 e an invite with a Google Hangout link. Once the session started and we are
  both in\, I will give you a brief intro about myself so that we can jump r
 ight into whatever you have in mind. Hopefully\, you can take as much as po
 ssible out of this session.<br><br>&nbsp\;<br><br>Looking forward to meetin
 g you<br><br>Renato Tarantelli<br><br><br><br>Location: This is a Google Me
 et web conference.<br>You can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet
 \, or smartphone.<br><a href="https://calendly.com/events/GOCCIYHOK5HBUO7L/
 google_meet">https://calendly.com/events/GOCCIYHOK5HBUO7L/google_meet</a><b
 r><br>Please share anything that will help us to have a great conversation:
  Specify your challenge\, list questions\, etc.:<br><br>Hello Renato \,<br>
 Nice to meet you here.<br>My name is Zufar. I am a java/kotlin backend deve
 loper from Moscow\, Russia.<br>https://www.linkedin.com/in/zufar-sunagatov/
 <br><br>My current desire is to move to Germany and improve my IT knowledge
 .<br><br>If it is possible\, I would like to ask you to help me. May be you
  can recommend something and help me.<br>1) how I can learn AWS\, Docker\, 
 Kubernetes\, CI/CD. I want to understand how to work with them\, because a 
 lot of job positions require these technologies.<br>2) how I can solve algo
 rithm tasks in Leetcode\, Algoexpert effectively to pass an interview in FA
 ANG in the future.<br>3) how I can improve my knowledge of Java\, Kotlin\, 
 Sring Boot framework\, Postgres database\, SQL to develop modern applicatio
 ns.<br>4) how I can improve my understanding of Microservice architecture. 
 I want to know how to develop perfect architecture.<br>5) how I can improve
  my CV and LinkedIn profile to be interesting for recruters and IT companie
 s.<br>6) how I can improve my career path. I can imagine that it is good id
 ea to move to the USA because there are a lot of interesting companies\, pr
 ojects\, people and so on. I would like to discuss it.<br>7) how I can relo
 cate to Europe or The USA. May be I use LinkedIn and speak with recruters i
 n wrong way. I would like to discuss it either.<br><br>If we can discuss on
 e of these questions\, write me please\, I will prepare questions for this 
 topic.<br><br>Best Regards<br>Zufar Sunagatov<br><br>Need to make changes t
 o this event?<br>Cancel: <a href="https://calendly.com/cancellations/GOE4GH
 5XYQZUFFXO">https://calendly.com/cancellations/GOE4GH5XYQZUFFXO</a><br>Resc
 hedule: <a href="https://calendly.com/reschedulings/GOE4GH5XYQZUFFXO">https
 ://calendly.com/reschedulings/GOE4GH5XYQZUFFXO</a><br><br>Powered by Calend
 ly.com\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/yvr-
 kpoq-zpt\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/an
 swer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
