DESCRIPTION:Event Name: The Mentoring Club - Session with Nagaraddi\n\nHi!\
 n\nThanks for subscribing for a mentoring session with me. We are excited t
 o get to know you and work with you on your current challenge.\n\n \n\nWhat
 's next?\n\nPlease select the date and time that works best for you. Once y
 ou’ve selected your slot you'll receive an invite with a Google Hangout lin
 k. Once the session started and we are both in\, I will give you a brief in
 tro about myself so that we can jump right into whatever you have in mind. 
 Hopefully you can take as much as possible out of this session.\n\n \n\nLoo
 king forward to meet you\n\nNagaraddi\n\nLocation: This is a Google Meet we
 b conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or s
 martphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/AOHEITTOMTTZKDIO/google_meet\n\nPle
 ase share anything that will help us to have a great conversation: Specify 
 your challenge\, list questions etc. *:\nHello! My name is Zufar.\nI am an 
 Java/Kotlin software engineer from Moscow\, Russia.\nhttps://www.linkedin.c
 om/in/zufar-sunagatov/\nI would like to grow as a professional\, so I need 
 a mentor to define my development path.\nI mean that there are a lot of cou
 rces\, certification and companies where I can grow from a common backend d
 eveloper to CTO of big company. I would like to discuss possible ways which
  steps I should pass.\n\nNeed to make changes to this event?\nCancel: https
 ://calendly.com/cancellations/AKHZCEIPCUY37IN2\nReschedule: https://calendl
 y.com/reschedulings/AKHZCEIPCUY37IN2\n\nPowered by Calendly.com\n\n\n-::~:~
 ::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::
 ~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/fgz-woqy-cpd\n\nLear
 n more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\n
 Please do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
