ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;CN=dax@se
 archxrecruitment.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:dax@searchxrecruitment.com
ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;CN=zufar.
 sunagatov@gmail.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:zufar.sunagatov@gmail.com
CREATED:20230510T101132Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Name: 30 Minute Meeting\n\nPlease share anything that wil
 l help prepare for our meeting.:\nDax L. 3:52 PM\nHigh performance\, low la
 tency\, financial markets… Are you ready to make a difference in trading ☁️
  Zufar?\nGood afternoon ☁️ Zufar\, Currently\, I am exclusively looking for
  a skilled Trading Reliability Engineer\, for a high-frequency trading comp
 any in Amsterdam. As a High-Frequency trading firm\, it breathes technology
 . For every trader on the floor\, there are at least two developers. Make n
 o mistake\, IT is their core business. Because in such a highly competitive
  market\, performance\, speed\, and reliability are key. This is where you 
 come in. As their Trading Reliability Engineer\, you will play a critical r
 ole at the heart of their complex environment. Making sure that they can re
 lease daily in a safe and controlled manner is a crucial part of the role a
 s well as ensuring high availability\, stability\, and performance. You wil
 l be troubleshooting and providing quick responses to production issues but
  more importantly\, you will solve the root cause of problems in a structur
 al way. As mentioned earlier\, your particular skill set and experience hav
 e caught my attention. https://searchxrecruitment.com/en/job/trading-reliab
 ility-engineer-4485/ I am very curious about your background\, your ambitio
 ns\, and what your dream job looks like. I always put a lot of time and eff
 ort into getting to know my clients and their needs. In this way\, I can pa
 int a better picture of the position\, the organization\, and the people wh
 o work there in a personal conversation. I believe that this is the only wa
 y to provide our candidates with substantial insight into the company's cul
 ture and create a perfect match. I look forward to hearing from you\, Dax L
 ouwris Executive Search Consultant | Search X Recruitment | IT\n\nNeed to m
 ake changes to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/0f37
 8e98-08cc-439d-86a8-a7d6bf2daeee\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedu
 lings/0f378e98-08cc-439d-86a8-a7d6bf2daeee\n\nPowered by Calendly.com\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20230510T104001Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Zufar Sunagatov and Dax Louwris
