 /p><p>engineering capability and developed solutions</p><p>• Mentor and coa
 ch developers on software principles and best practices</p><p>• Ensure desi
 gn decisions align with business objectives\, technical requirements\,</p><
 p>and target architecture</p><p>• Collaborate with Domain and Solution Arch
 itects to ensure consistency across the</p><p>enterprise</p><p>• Document a
 nd communicate design decisions and reasoning</p><p>• Support the developme
 nt of technical standards and guidelines</p><p>• Participate in technical d
 ecisions and take an active role in the decision making</p><p>process</p><p
 >• Ensure compliance with security\, operational\, and development policies
 <b><i>Reasons why this job would be interesting to you:</i></b></p><p>• And
 ersen cooperates with such businesses as Samsung\, Reuter Gruppe\, T-</p><p
 >Systems\, TUI\, Ryanair\, Johnson &amp\; Johnson\, etc. This project is ju
 st your beginning here</p><p>– working with us means reliability and prospe
 cts.</p><p>• We have been strengthening our expertise since 2007.</p><p>• W
 e welcome specialists from every part of the world.</p><p>• Salaries at And
 ersen are pegged to the EUR\, and our employees are provided with</p><p>a b
 enefit package and an extensive set of bonuses.</p><p>• We give our employe
 es an opportunity to attend and participate in the company’s</p><p>BA meetu
 ps\, as well as offer a compensation program for international professional
 </p><p>certificates.</p><p>• There are many different ways to grow and deve
