DESCRIPTION:<h1>Your Zoom Interview with Hazelcast</h1><h3><table><tbody><t
 r><td><p>Hi Zufar\,</p><p>Thanks for confirming your availability. You are 
 now booked in to speak with our hiring team in more detail. <br><br>You wil
 l be meeting Ed Thurman and Daniel Young</p><p>The interview is scheduled f
 or 5:30pm on Wednesday 10 December 2025 (Greenwich Mean Time). It should la
 st 45 minutes.<br><a href="https://track.pstmrk.it/3s/hazelcast.pinpointhq.
 com%2Fcandidates%2Finterview_parts%2FifckczmGBwLNjcktFRe6FK4g%2Fjoin/h0sH/p
 d7BAQ/AQ/ab2632f2-32b2-4264-88d4-28c35f79d828/1/YzwJDljDLP" target="_blank"
 >Join meeting on Zoom</a></p><p></p><p>This interview will be with a member
 (s) of our hiring team and will take place via Video call. You will be aske
 d more detailed questions about your experience that relates to our vacancy
 . This will include questions that will give you the opportunity to discuss
  how you can demonstrate your skills and knowledge\, as well as some techni
 cal aspects of the role.<br><br></p><p>We'd also encourage you to visit our
  website to familiarize yourself with Hazelcast. Also\, check out our Linke
 dIn page for the most up-to-date news on our Company.<br><br></p><p>Please 
 make sure you are in a location with a strong internet connection with as l
 ittle background noise as possible.<br><br></p><p>We are proud to be an equ
 al opportunities employer and believe we find our strength in our diversity
 . If you require any accommodation to assist you in the interview process\,
