DESCRIPTION:<b>Booked by</b>\nZufar Sunagatov\nzufar.sunagatov@gmail.com\n0
 7405503609\n<br><p>Thank you for scheduling a time to chat! Please add your
  name\, email address and phone number in the subject line manually under (
 your name here)\,email address and (your number here).</p><p>In the meantim
 e\, please send over an updated resume and the names of any people you know
  at Google (either socially or professionally) that would be very helpful.<
 /p><p>Please note\, our chat is NOT an interview or technical conversation.
  My goal is to learn more about you and your experience to see how we can f
 ind a good fit here at Google.</p><p>Please also note that I may ring you a
  few minutes past the scheduled call time and that I have a hard stop time 
 at the thirty minute mark. Also\, please choose an appointment slot at leas
 t one hour prior so I know it's on my calendar in case I'm in a meeting bef
 orehand.</p><p>Please provide me with the following information prior to ou
 r phone call.</p><p>[Please email your responses to renataw<a href="mailto:
 YourName@google.com" target="_blank"><u>@google.com</u></a>\, thanks!]</p><
 p>1. Legal first and last name:</p><p>2. Best email and phone number to rea
 ch you:</p><p>3. Strongest area of expertise (Android\, Backend\, iOS\, Ful
 lstack\, ML\, Front End\, Etc..)</p><p>4. On average what percentage of the
  time do you spend coding during your work day?</p><p>5. Strongest coding l
 anguage for interviews:</p><p>6. Google office location options you will co
 nsider (in order of preference):</p><p>7. What time frame would you be inte
 rested in potentially beginning the interview process at Google (ie. a coup
 le of weeks\, one\, two\, three months etc)?:</p><p>8. Do you currently nee
 d\, or will you someday require\, Google to sponsor work (if so\, type of V
 isa and expiration date):</p><p>Looking forward to chatting soon!</p><p>Ren
 ata Walczak</p><p>Expert Talent Advisor Supporting Google</p>
