DESCRIPTION:<table><tbody><tr><td>We are excited to meet you<hr /></td></tr
 ><tr><td>Dear Zufar\,<br><br>We are pleased to confirm that your interview 
 is scheduled for Fri\, 05 Dec\, 2025 at 03:00 PM Europe/London. At the sche
 duled time\, please connect using the Zoom link below.<br><b>Note: This wil
 l be a video interview conducted via Zoom\, so please be camera ready (ensu
 re you have a stable internet connection\, good lighting in the room\, and 
 that your camera is turned on with your face clearly visible). Please have 
 your Digital Interview Badge ready to show to your interviewer for verifica
 tion on the day of your interview (Printed/Hard copy is NOT needed).</b><br
 ><br>Please access the below link(s) for relevant details in preparation pr
 ior to the meeting:<br><a href="https://careers.oracle.com/en/sites/jobsear
 ch/jobs/preview/303294" target="_blank">Job Description</a> <br><a href="ht
 tps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BV0GMCITXg4" target="_blank">Oracle Careers</
 a> <br><br><br>Your badge is attached and will be required for all your sch
 eduled interviews. Please have your badge ready to present to your intervie
 wer for verification on the day. This badge is mandatory as part of the Ora
 cle interview process and will be verified by each interviewer at the start
  of every interview (Printed/Hard copy is NOT needed). Make sure that you h
 ave a stable internet connection\, proper room lighting\, and your camera t
 urned on with your image clearly visible to the interviewer. At the schedul
 ed time\, please connect using the Zoom link below.<br><br>After your inter
 view\, your recruiter will meet with the hiring team and notify you of thei
 r decision and any next steps.<br><br><br><br>Please click <a href="https:/
 /hrservices.oracle.com/apex/recruit_ns_ext/calendar/meeting/41206682324F46A
 4390937C0DC12178FA074D652234D7471E13D910B0261E0FEAFF7772E7BDB48C0D510D5035D
 D4B56AC3B0061FFEA8644B0356E8F6E0907B84" target="_blank">here</a> to add the
  meeting to your calendar.<br><br>Please reach out to Petr Spurek (<a href=
 "mailto:petr.spurek@oracle.com" target="_blank">petr.spurek@oracle.com</a>)
 \, with any questions.<br><br><br><br><b>Would you like to receive SMS Upda
 tes about the Interview schedules?</b><br>Please follow these steps to opt 
 in for SMS:<br>1. Go to our <a href="https://careers.oracle.com/jobs/#en/si
 tes/jobsearch/my-profile/sign-in" target="_blank">career site</a> and click
  on the Person icon at the top right of the screen\, then sign in with Emai
 l or Phone Number. You will be prompted to enter a verification code.<br>2.
  Click on 'Info and Alerts' and 'Edit Personal Information'.<br>3. Enter yo
 ur phone number. Click on save and verify. You will be prompted to enter a 
 verification code.<br>4. Once verified check the box 'Use SMS as communicat
 ion channel' then click 'update' at the bottom so your changes will be refl
 ected on your profile.<br><br><b>Your Voice Matters</b><br>You have a voice
  in helping us create the best candidate experience possible. During the in
 terview process\, we'll send you a one-minute survey about your experience.
  Please take a moment to share your feedback. We value your input and are a
 lways open to improving how we do things.<br><br><i>Oracle is an Equal Empl
 oyment Opportunity Employer committed to diversity and inclusion. For more 
 information\, please see our <a href="https://www.oracle.com/corporate/care
