DESCRIPTION:Hi Zufar\,\n\nThank you for confirming your availability with u
 s.\n\nI'm pleased to confirm your next meeting for the Senior Backend Devel
 oper role\, via Google Meet has been scheduled for: \n\nTime/Date:\n3:30pm 
 BST on Thursday\, 31st July 2025\n\nDuration: \nUp to 2.5 hours\n\nAttendee
 : \nEdison Yap (Team Lead)\nLeonardo Donelli (Team Lead) \n\nWhat to expect
 :\nThe tech stage is up to 2.5 hours (including a 10-minute break)\n\nIt's 
 usually a brief intro from everyone. They will ask you for more details and
  dig deeper into your intro.\n\nFollowing that\, there are some open theore
 tical questions\, which can range from high-level to low-level\, including 
 how the web works and its fundamentals. \n\nThere will be live coding\, the
 n database/SQL and finally some system design work 😍 \n\n\n💡 We suggest l
 ogging into the meeting 5 minutes early to verify that your camera and micr
 ophone are functioning correctly.\n\nPlease don't hesitate to contact me if
  you have any questions or feel there is anything I can help with. \n\nKind
  regards\,\nKit Yi Christine Wong\nFresha\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google
